  "title": "Are bruchids field pests of chickpea",
  "abstract": "Species of Callosobruchus are important pests of stored chickpeas [Cicer arietinum]. In extensive surveys on pods and seeds from India and elsewhere, no evidence was found that infestation originates on growing plants in the field.",
